Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.80,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur4.5\pos(1177.5,780)}她不擅烹飪 她招惹蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央 身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴 你戴歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}可以開始烹調了 同學們小心用菜刀和火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:31.51,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}先來決定誰要負責什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}畫鬼腳圖決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}其實我不太擅長做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大概會引起爆炸 或是燒焦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以想做不會焦掉的沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不用擔心喔 那央
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這些都不是什麼太難的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}畫好了 來選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.27,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)\bord0\1c&H52534E&\frz340.7\pos(201,759)}沙拉&餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.27,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)\bord0\1c&H52534E&\frz341.1\pos(1125,690)}漢\N堡\N排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.27,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)\bord0\1c&H52534E&\frz341.1\pos(1566,840)}咖\N哩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}圭 最容易失敗的是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}漢堡排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就這一條 這條最不像漢堡排了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:26.75,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}老天老天 給我沙拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我選右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}剩下的就給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要開了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來 這是給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}做漢堡排要放洋蔥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你總該有吃過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不就是把絞肉揉~在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}弄~成一團 烤~成一塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央沒在家裡做過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}因為小時候幫忙炸可樂餅時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}把醋和油搞混了 變成大悲劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就一直有心理陰影了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這一般會弄混嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}後來為了不給家人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我就不再去廚房了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那你也沒有切過洋蔥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再切成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以我就說不會做菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼啦 聲音好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}切到手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沿著洋蔥縱向纖維小心地切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別把纖維切開來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}縱向？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼切…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}切起來好切就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對對 就擺出小貓手的姿勢慢慢切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再將洋蔥橫放 從頭用一樣的切法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}冷靜下來就沒問題 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央 跟你說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}等一下 我現在很專注
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 要用微波爐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}切洋蔥前先用微波爐稍稍加熱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就不容易變成那個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早點告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}剛剛就想說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}把椒鹽加入絞肉裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這種噁心的舒適感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}噁心的舒適感？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}感覺介於噁心和舒服之間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}第一次有這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再加入炒過的洋蔥和雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央 輕敲兩下就能敲碎殼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}把這些混合均勻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再加入牛奶和泡水的小麥粉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這真的能做成漢堡排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}輕輕擠一點牛奶進去比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}滑嫩很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}將肉餡四等分 捏成橢圓形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}放在掌心上拍打 除掉空氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是把肉團放在兩手間丟來丟去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了 好像有在電視上看過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}四等分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央真熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這根本易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是圭的份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 肉胚完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有一個是心形的呢 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這裡面灌注了我的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只是記號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}噹噹噹噹 沙拉油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這次我可不會搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一般人都不會搞錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個 大湯匙是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 小湯匙借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 咖哩裡要加蜂蜜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}味道會溫和不少的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但不煮透點 咖哩的黏稠感就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼你還知道這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你是哪家的閨女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼嘛 煎漢堡排不是挺簡單的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}感覺真不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我拿去洗了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 真琴 餅乾做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還沒 現在要讓麵團發酵一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}之後捏出形狀再烤一下就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}魔女做的餅乾 肯定很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}確實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒有啦 別給我提高難度啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有沒有魔女傳統餅乾之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}雖然說不上傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但倒是有很好玩的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}叫做魔女的小指
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}魔女的小指？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}如名字一樣 以魔女小指為模型的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}可是魔女間結緣的點心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是什麼 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼機會難得 我就做幾個試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}剛好材料齊全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好啊 我也想嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央 要煎焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}應該好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}總算完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}第一次就能做成這樣很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央很有做菜的天賦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一放鬆就立刻覺得餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴 你手上拿什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不對 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}手…手指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是剛剛說的魔女的小指呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個是餅乾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對啊 指甲是杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}訣竅就在於要做得以假亂真才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真實得可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}烤過後會更像真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這就是結緣點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還以為是更可愛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 做完的組可以品嚐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咖哩完工 接下來就是上交了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}辛苦了 趕快開動吧 快餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這下可能會吃很多碗飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}又沒關係 都那麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 今天就當獎勵自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}誰負責煮飯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}阿圭 我該帶什麼去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想想…先帶上工作手套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這種打扮可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只要不怕會弄髒的話都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大清早的是要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們去給蘋果疏果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}疏果？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是摘蘋果花的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你大概弄錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}反正去了就懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}茜姐也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}去吧 反正也沒事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}耶 和茜姐一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們幾個 該出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真舒服的風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}聞起來真香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}現在開到什麼程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}五成盛開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏真厲害 什麼都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴姐才厲害 還能在天上飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}雙臂一張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安 哪家的女孩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我親戚家的孩子 今天來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}多可人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}婆婆說你可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 還有外國人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別看我這樣 其實我是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想今天疏完這園子的果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}手腳俐落點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就拜託各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這給你們用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真漂亮呢 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 美極了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}蘋果樹長得可真矮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}老爸說就是靠修枝來讓果樹橫向生長的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此 放著不管就會長很大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 枝條橫向生長也比較方便作業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在園子裡走路時記得左顧右盼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別一頭撞上枝條了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼 撞到頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還在看花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}人家剛說完 你到底在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴真是個冒失鬼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}走路時可要好好看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們去哪裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你地就去果度啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}摘蔬果呢樣野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看唔看到尼度生左一堆花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}每朵花都會結出蘋果來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但系如果全部都結曬果 咁樣就結唔出好蘋果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以要令到啲養分都去曬一朵花度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就好似咁樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}留低中間生得最好既花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}其它全部摘曬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你地看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明未啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}抱歉 我只聽懂第一句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}句子一長就不太懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}伯伯 說日語啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼突然說法語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}尼啲就系日文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}仲系聽唔明方言啊…圭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這些花都會長成蘋果的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過所有花都結果的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就會有些品相不好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以需要疏花 來讓養分集中在一朵上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}將中央長得最好的花留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}其它都摘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}摘下的花可以扔掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 丟在腳邊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們沒能長成蘋果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}殘酷的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別說這種話啦 感覺像做了大壞事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}它們大概還會化作土壤的養分哺育新果的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哥哥 我來摘上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏好帥氣呀 小忍者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎 那我以後當忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 不是魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對喔 那就當魔女忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是什麼 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過魔女也能是忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 我也來摘上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 小心點呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}風景真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}叫我姐姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 這裡差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}搞定了嗎 梯子借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下去的時候倒有點可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你平時可是飛得更高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這跟飛翔又不一樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}阿圭 那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是角額壁蜂的蜂箱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}蜜蜂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我找找…有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是這個小傢伙 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題嗎 不會被螫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒事的 它不螫人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}角額壁蜂在採集花粉當養分時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也會為蘋果花授粉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以放個蜂箱 請它們幫忙做事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}角額壁蜂可真偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我能碰碰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}小小的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}它走到指尖就會飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好痛好痛 它咬好大力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}它們心情不好時也會咬人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我還是第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不螫人而是咬人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還是早點放開比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂 歇一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別笑我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}打擾一下 這是我昨天在學校做的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不介意的話請嚐嚐看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}手指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}和你的手指一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}吃了這種餅乾 就會有好緣分喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}蜜蜂就是因此才咬你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}人家蜜蜂親了你一口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來沾沾看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊 蜂蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這也是緣分呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有緣真好
